These scripts are in-use throughout cashmusic.org, but need tweaks and
updates before being released publicly. The general idea is that there's
a single master JS object that serves as namespace and controller for
any number of smaller script modules. It also launches external scripts
as needed, and can auto-attach behaviors to elements. 

The 1.0 version of Flower will focus on SoundPlayer, adding HTML5 
capabilities and more flexible playlist and event functionality. 